  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "CRANE & HOIST OPERATOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure regular maintenance on his assigned crane i.e. properly greased, lubricated and regularly cleaned as to allow the crane stay operational at all times;</li><li>Ensure before starting work, Crane Operator is to conduct daily safety check on his assigned crane including filling-up crane log book and lifting log book as per Ministry of Manpower guideline;</li><li>Ensure appropriate valid lifting gears are used;</li><li>Ensure to adhere site in-house regulations i.e. to hand-over the by-pass key to site lifting supervisor or site person in-charge prior execution of the job to avoid any safety violation;</li><li>Report to Controller and/or Operation Staff for advice if there is any unsafe job requested by site;</li><li>Ensure timely submission of completed Job Sheet or Time Sheet or Work Order;</li><li>Follow operational procedures with due care and diligence;</li><li>Undertake any other assignment related to his scope of work assigned by the HOD and/or Management whenever deemed necessary.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li>Possess valid crane operator licence from MOM with at least 1 year experience;</li><li>Punctual and hardworking;</li><li>Reliable team player.</li></ol><p>Interested, please apply now or call us at <strong>6799 5934 / 6799 5949</strong></p>",
